column2: Fangdd Network Group Ltd. is a property technology company. The company is headquartered in Shenzhen, Guangdong and currently employs 1,655 full-time employees. SaaS-based solutions connect real estate agents with essential business resources, including customers, property listings, capital and transaction data. The platform matches agents with the listings as well as buyers, sellers, landlords, renters. The firm operates its businesses primarily in the China market.
